v 3
d 'CLEARLAB': module to clear all labels and notes
d
d {cmd:clearlab} removes all labels and notes from the dataset in memory. It is
d especially useful when imported data has some of these characteristics that
d are not going to be used, and thus clean slate is preferred.
d
d KW: labels
d KW: value labels
d KW: notes
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260608
d
d Author: Gorkem Aksaray, Trinity College Dublin
d Support: aksarayg@tcd.ie
d
f clearlab.ado
f clearlab.sthlp
